entry.title: Is this year independence day is 76th or 77th? Here’s the Answer
entry.summary: Many of us thinking and having doubt that whether 15 August 2023 is the 76th or 77th Independence Day, the sentiment is unchanging, but it’s crucial to fully comprehend the root of this confusion. There are two different schools of thought when it comes to counting the years between the historical day 1947 and the present. The post Is this year independence day is 76th or 77th?
